---
title: Smashed Taco Bacon Crunchburgers with Guacamole & Tortilla Chips
description: The latest burgers from our burger lab are seasoned with our vibrant blend of fajita-style spices, then smashed directly in the hot pan for crispy, craggy edges and an extra-juicy finish. Add colorful toppings, like guacamole, hot sauce, and crushed blue tortilla chips for extra crunch, and make burger night an instant fiesta (in a flash!).
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/660c631d9149ba03ec9b06a2-4da9f9c7.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/671011ae5e99f1b6964352de-en-US.pdf
author: HelloFresh
time required: 15 minutes
servings: 2
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/smashed-taco-bacon-crunchburgers-671011ae5e99f1b6964352de
course: main course
cuisine: Central America
nutrition:
  calories: 1110 kcal
